															<p class="category">Breakdown: Mental Health</p>
																						<h2 class="title">Closed community spaces due to coronavirus will leave the homeless out in the cold &#8212; it’s a disgrace</h2>
													</div>
					</div>
									<div class="item ">
						<div class="item-wrapper">
															<a href="https://calmatters.org/commentary/gov-newsom-wants-to-overhaul-californias-mental-health-care-system-heres-a-plan-for-that/" class="link thumb" aria-label="Read more about Gov. Newsom wants to overhaul California&#8217;s mental health care system. Here’s a plan for that">
									<div class="thumb-inner">
										<img width="326" height="214" src="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?fit=326%2C214" class="attachment-medium-wide-rec size-medium-wide-rec wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=1280 1280w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=300 300w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=768 768w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=460 460w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=326 326w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=780 780w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=860 860w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/iStock-912219896-1-e1558398753429.jpg?w=807 807w" sizes="(max-width: 326px) 100vw, 326px" />									</div>
								</a>
							
															<p class="category">Breakdown: Mental Health</p>
																						<h2 class="title">Gov. Newsom wants to overhaul California&#8217;s mental health care system. Here’s a plan for that</h2>
													</div>
					</div>
									<div class="item ">
						<div class="item-wrapper">
